  • Green marks new instructions to the Rabbit 2000.
  • Red marks new instructions replacing earlier ones for the Rabbit 2000.
  • Orange marks instructions present but undocumented in Rabbit 2000 and documented for the Rabbit 3000.
  • Pink background marks undocumented instructions.
  • Plum background marks duplicate instructions.
